						<summary>

						<p>Stone (No. 3) lying in the compound of the local court.</p>						

						<p>1708 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This damaged record registers a gift of land in Chikke Soṇḍūr to Jamunāgiri Bāvā by Hire Hindūrāya.</p>						

						<p>It is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1630, Sarvadhāri, Chaitra śu. 1</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1708 A.D., March, 12</hi> The details cannot, however, be verified.</p>						

						</summary>
